{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"623","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"10年減碳計畫效應 英國綠能業大缺工12萬人","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-02-01 13:30 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>聯合晚報 編譯徐榆涵／綜合報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%A2%E5%B2%B8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%BB.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 561px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>英國需在<span lang='EN-US'>2030</span>年前填補綠色能源產業中的<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>萬個職缺，圖為英國離岸風力發電場。 路透</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>英國國家電網公司（<span lang='EN-US'>National Grid</span>）警告，政府若想達成具法律約束力的氣候變遷目標，英國必須在<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年內招募逾<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>萬人填補綠色能源的職缺。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>衛報報導，國家電網公司的研究報告發現，英國需要在<span lang='EN-US'>2030</span>年前填補綠色能源產業中的<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>萬個職缺，以幫助開發能減少溫室氣體排放量至接近零的計畫。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>該報告指出，這個職缺人數到<span lang='EN-US'>2050</span>年時可能會達到<span lang='EN-US'>40</span>萬個，屆時英國政府預期已開發出以再生能源電力、綠色加熱系統和電動汽車為基礎的乾淨能源系統。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報告警告，能源產業有五分之一員工將在<span lang='EN-US'>2030</span>年退休。英國能源產業面臨其他產業的激烈競爭，且追求<span lang='EN-US'>STEM</span>（科學、技術、工程和數學）資格的年輕人變少。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>英國計畫將溫室氣體排放量降至幾近為零，並透過碳捕捉計畫抵銷不可避免的汙染，此舉將需要大量投資離岸風力發電、乾淨加熱系統、電動汽車和碳捕捉技術。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>YouGov</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>著手的研究發現，英國所有地區的各個年齡層民眾都「尋求具有環保意義的工作」。每<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>名男、女性民眾中，分別有超過七人和八人表示，他們渴望在對抗氣候變遷中發揮所長。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>且超過半數成年人特意尋找為英國實現氣候目標的組織工作。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報告說，綠色能源工作日益增加的需求，可能為「遍布全國每個地區」的熟練技工、工程師和其他專家帶來機會。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4315470</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-03","clk_count":"181"}},"__N_SSG":true}